Waelstow
========
    [wel sto ä]  / *noun* 
    
    1) literal: "death field" or "slaugher field"; 
    2) Anglo Saxon term for battlefields
    3) A collection of Python testing utilties

Installation
============

.. code-block:: bash

    $ pip install waelstow

Supports
========

Tested with Python 3.7 - Python 3.11

